1915 Çanakkale Bridge, Turkey 🇹🇷
1915 Çanakkale Bridge is a suspension bridge being built between Lapseki and Gelibolu districts of Çanakkale province in Turkey. It will be the first suspension bridge of the Dardanelles Strait and the fifth of the Marmara Region. Wikipedia
Total length: 3,563 m
Height from water: 69 m
Width: 43m
Start-End date: 18 March 2017-18 March 2022

Total budget: 3,563 m
Sudan road: 69 m
